Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是学习柔和控制Mana的魔法入门
